                        </div>
                        <div class="sm2-col">
                            <a href="http://figubbrazlevic.bandcamp.com/track/bosnian-syndicate" target="_blank" title="Buy &quot;Bosnian Syndicate&quot;" class="sm2-icon sm2-cart">Buy this track</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="sm2-col">
